<p><b>Industry Visits and Industrial Trainings:</b> On the demands of Colleges we arrange for Industry Visits and Industrial Training Programs for final year students with the help of corporate available in Pune and around. They can show their caliber to work on live projects & get absorbed in jobs.</p>

